sub_title: Seismic Interpreter - Structural Geologist at Shell, NAM
summary:
I consider geology as both my profession and as a hobby. At the NAM/Shell I am assigned to the land asset team as structural geologist/geophysicist. Project management and business development support are also part of my daily work.

I have an easygoing and open minded personality. I am a true team player, willing to help and advise people, and always in for a challenge.  

Being a perfectionist it is my objective to deliver sound work and to achieve maximum customer satisfaction. 

My personal goal is to become an outstanding geologist by improving my skills in the various disciplines geology has to offer. My curiosity and perseverance will help me to achieve this goal.
